-- U.S. Stocks Extend Gains as Genzyme Rallies on Reports of Offer
-- Michael P. Regan
-- 2010-07-23T17:30:14Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-23/u-s-stocks-extend-gains-as-genzyme-rallies-on-reports-of-offer.html

          
          
             U.S. stocks extended gains as
Genzyme Corp. rallied on reports that the drugmaker has been
approached with a takeover offer from Sanofi-Aventis SA.  
 Genzyme rallied 19 percent after the Wall Street Journal
and CNBC reported the takeover talks.  
          
          


  


        